{"tid":123230,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"古巨基岩岩出左翻唱歌<最愛>連係英國拍既MV","createTime":"2017-02-16T16:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T15:50:04.000Z","uid":9030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc97f980c9264a363b244cb64aeb225605ee2d87","tid":123230,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"&lt;最愛&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lea6gusazHI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlea6gusazHI&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=77a2bf8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lea6gusazHI</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.eegmusic.com/upload/news/photo/2017/02/68052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eegmusic.com%2Fupload%2Fnews%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F68052.jpg&h=e8b88575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作曲／詞：李宗盛/鍾曉陽,張艾嘉<br />\n改編詞：鄭國江<br />\n編曲：Jim Ling<br />\n監製：舒文@Zoo Music<br />\n<br />\n* 若你永遠為這一縷愛　為了愛過願意不再改<br />\n這生盼只有此夢　一生只想得你愛<br />\n共你挽住了握過了　願你挽住再不放開<br />\n千般溫柔這纖纖手　萬縷熱愛在滲透 *<br />\n<br />\nRepeat *<br />\n<br />\nAh...<br />\n恨事遺留始終不朽　千金一笑瀟灑依舊<br />\n對對錯錯千般恩怨　像湖水吹皺<br />\n曾被愛過痛過的我　曾被愛過痛過的你<br />\n原為了要我與你遇見　再度分開<br />\n<br />\n要說的偏偏忘掉　我最愛的人　今生只得你　永遠也得你<br />\n要說的偏偏忘掉　最愛我的人　今生只得你　永遠也得你<br />\n情是這樣細膩 (估唔到你同我一樣)"},{"pid":"2d2a38a6ec25541c40388a4eacbb0a71032aca55","tid":123230,"uid":16047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"東京事變"},{"pid":"11f6f23e02d3698417d9f12099b5887bd771f291","tid":123230,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"古巨基即將推出的致敬哥哥大碟《SALUTE TO DEAR LESLIE》，重新演繹10首哥哥於不同年代的經典作品。這首改編作品，原曲為台灣女歌手潘越雲的同名作品，由李宗盛先生作曲，後來由鄭國江老師填詞成為廣東版，收錄在1988年張國榮的《Virgin Snow》專輯。歌曲結構非主流格調，沒有特定的副歌部分，意境凄美，配上一份描述對舊愛執迷的歌詞，予人不輕言放手的感覺。歌曲結構充滿起伏，充滿舞台戲劇性的情緒反差，最後以一句對白「估唔到你同我一樣」完結，以當時傳統港式流行曲對比來說，算是偏鋒的作品。雖然沒有正式派過台，但哥哥先後在1988及1997年演唱會上都有選唱過，可見對其情有獨鍾，而這次古巨基選唱此曲，也是鍾情那份歌曲張力的獨特感。"},{"pid":"2fba9cfadd3ad3f2ecc8909eacaf2c48ac68c659","tid":123230,"uid":12591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"等到頸都長埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09e9862fc541c8a93b475b5634bf6d93775152c","tid":123230,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"無法提供此影片，得我睇唔到？"},{"pid":"758184af1713d36df599f5ca25d9fed670c877b1","tid":123230,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無法提供此影片，得我睇唔到？</blockquote><br />\n應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611df692cbf4997c7c947ca98e7cdb0c1820ea37","tid":123230,"uid":36683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出完唔該快D出返新廣東歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5772efc786bb12c05057b1985b9cc142de6f92af","tid":123230,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出完唔該快D出返新廣東歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cc3a715486ff8bd9874718d982d4bdc4c7f205","tid":123230,"uid":12591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T19:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出完唔該快D出返新廣東歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順便開埋演唱會啦"},{"pid":"bbefd9d0a31a5651ec6a862a0d782a9017ca3005","tid":123230,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出完唔該快D出返新廣東歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順便開埋演唱會啦</blockquote><br />\nhope<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154c949ccd86e69a79d66380713040789e164e93","tid":123230,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"古巨基:<br />\n<br />\n雖然「最愛」當年在哥哥的《Virgin Snow》專輯中不算派台歌曲，但這次在《Salute to Dear Leslie》歌單中卻是我第一首選的歌曲。<br />\n這次製作的難度，對我和監製來說是要盡量注意唱腔，以免讓人有刻意模仿哥哥的感覺。<br />\n但，坦白說，哥哥的音樂陪著我成長，那時的每首歌包括哥哥演唱氣息上的一吞一吐，都根深蒂固的植在我腦𥚃。所以，如果你在我的演譯𥚃找到了某些哥哥的影子，請體諒這不是刻意模仿，這是對喜歡的人的不知不覺的潛移默化。"},{"pid":"ef29195f8d50ddf4a722cca27283ca10f45715ef","tid":123230,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"古巨基致敬張國榮專輯音樂會<br />\n3月16日 20:00<br />\n浸會大學會堂"},{"pid":"2c13425441e40e4fdb5ee284df6f4d40aebfaf96","tid":123230,"uid":36683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古巨基致敬張國榮專輯音樂會<br />\n3月16日 20:00<br />\n浸會大學會堂</blockquote><br />\n久違既音樂會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9b61bad8f2a6665cfd65496af3189083736b6e","tid":123230,"uid":73057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"原全認唔到係佢把聲, 又唔好聽.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以俾番歡樂今宵, 傷追人, 愛得太遲個佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25601aea2a1e4e5014f44d4a64435a1666fe9391","tid":123230,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原全認唔到係佢把聲, 又唔好聽.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以俾番歡樂今宵, 傷追人, 愛得太遲個佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/